'27:53': [
{sup:1, word:"came", lines:["In the type, the firstfruits of the harvest ({Lev23:10|Lev. 23:10}-{Lev23:11|11}) were not a single stalk of wheat but a sheaf of wheat, typifying not only the resurrected Christ but also the saints who were raised from the dead after His resurrection, as seen here.","All the things listed in vv. {Mat27:51|51}-{Mat27:53|53} are different aspects of the excellent effect of the Lord&rsquo;s death."]},
{sup:2, word:"appeared", lines:["Where they went after this we have no way to trace."]},
],
